Yeah?

01:22.959 --> 01:25.411
Yeah.

01:27.005 --> 01:29.415
On my way.

01:33.052 --> 01:35.012
Seriously?

01:35.013 --> 01:37.723
It's a holiday.

01:37.724 --> 01:40.342
Bad guys don't take a holiday.

01:40.351 --> 01:42.887
Go back to sleep.

01:52.530 --> 01:54.565
[SIGHS]

01:55.784 --> 01:58.486
