02:08.838 --> 02:10.339
I was hoping we could talk.

02:10.340 --> 02:12.750
Yeah, I gotta go.

02:13.176 --> 02:15.177
So you're still upset?

02:15.178 --> 02:19.298
I'm not upset. I'm just late.

02:19.891 --> 02:22.343
Call you later?

