<i>♪ I've got to keep my image
While suspended on a throne ♪</i>

03:28.918 --> 03:32.713
<i>♪ That looks out upon my kingdom
With people all unknown ♪</i>

03:32.714 --> 03:36.592
<i>♪ Who imagine I'm not human
And my heart is made of stone ♪</i>

03:36.593 --> 03:40.262
<i>♪ And I've never had no problems
And my toilet's rimmed with gold ♪</i>

